params.text: Dodo dafa set Yaay.
Gis na fukki balooŋ.
Gis na juroom ñiétti kas.
Gis na juroom ñeeti kuddu.
Gis na juroom ñaari pañe.
Gis na juroom benni wás.
Gis na juroomi tóor-tóor.
Gis na ay ñeetti tubeey.
Gis na ñetti jumtukaayu misik.
Gis na ñaari loxo.
Dodo gis na benn yaay.

"Foowu Láqatu" credits

This work, "Foowu Láqatu", is a derivative of "Hide and Seek" written by All Children Reading Cambodia. © The Asia Foundation 2019, and used under CC BY. "Foowu Láqatu" is licensed under CC BY 4.0 by Curious Learning.
